OL,3,CWhat happens with 33C heat hits the
OL,4,CNorth West?
OL,6,FAs temperatures across the North West
OL,7,Fare set to reach as high as 33C,
OL,8,Femergency services, care providers and
OL,9,Fhealth organisations are stepping up
OL,10,Fpreparations to protect vulnerable
OL,11,Fpeople and prevent heat-related
OL,12,Fincidents.
OL,14,FThe UK Health Security Agency has
OL,15,Fissued an amber heat-health alert for
OL,16,Fthe region, warning that the hot
OL,17,Fweather could have significant impacts
OL,18,Fon health and social care services,
OL,19,Fparticularly for older people, those
OL,20,Fwith underlying health conditions and
OL,21,Fvulnerable groups.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
