CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782366482
OL,3,CWhat happens with 33C heat hits the
OL,4,CNorth West?
OL,6,FCare homes across the region are
OL,7,Fputting additional measures in place
OL,8,Fto ensure residents remain safe and
OL,9,Fcomfortable throughout the heatwave.
OL,11,FOlder people are particularly
OL,12,Fvulnerable to heat-related illnesses
OL,13,Fbecause they may not feel thirsty, may
OL,14,Fstruggle to regulate their body
OL,15,Ftemperature, or may be taking
OL,16,Fmedication that increases the risk of
OL,17,Fdehydration.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
