CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782366482
OL,3,CWhat happens with 33C heat hits the
OL,4,CNorth West?
OL,6,FAt Parkhaven Trust in Liverpool, staff
OL,7,Fare carrying out additional welfare
OL,8,Fchecks and closely monitoring
OL,9,Fresidents' fluid intake.
OL,11,FRegistered Manager Cassie Dickinson
OL,12,Fsaid: "It is important to remember
OL,13,Fthat they might not always realise
OL,14,Fthat it is as hot as it is or remember
OL,15,Fthat they need a drink.
OL,17,F"Some people lack the cognitive
OL,18,Fability to get a drink or open a
OL,19,Fwindow, so we have to be mindful about
OL,20,Fextra checks and making sure that
OL,21,Fpeople are kept cool and hydrated."
OL,26,@tD@GOUyD@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782366482
OL,3,CWhat happens with 33C heat hits the
OL,4,CNorth West?
OL,6,FShe said the organisation has several
OL,7,Fmeasures in place to help residents
OL,8,Fcope with the rising temperatures.
OL,10,F"We have climate controls, air
OL,11,Fconditioning, and we have big doors
OL,12,Fthat open to allow in some fresh air
OL,13,Fin.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782366482
OL,3,CWhat happens with 33C heat hits the
OL,4,CNorth West?
OL,6,F"We also allow for extra checks for
OL,7,Fhydration during any period of hot
OL,8,Fweather, so we will make sure that at
OL,9,Fleast, in between every call, that
OL,10,Fstaff are going in, encouraging them
OL,11,Fto drink fluids and documenting what
OL,12,Fpeople have had to drink so we can
OL,13,Fkeep an eye on what they have had to
OL,14,Fdrink throughout the day.
OL,16,F"We also encourage residents to spend
OL,17,Fsome time outside in the shade,
OL,18,Fbecause it gives them some fresh air
OL,19,Fand helps to cool them down as well."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
